uzino.Jak dotrzeć do Ścieżki Zdrowia? Kierujemy się ulicą Wilczka od centrum Luzina. W połowie drogi znajduje się wjazd do leśnego parkingu, położony na przeciwko supermarketu Biedronka.\n\n  z dnia: 2013-08-14 10:37  \n\n<p>&nbsp;</p><div class=\"gdlr-shortcode-wrapper\"><div class=\"gdlr-gallery-item gdlr-item\" ><div class=\"gallery-column three columns\"><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x460/F7n8d021D0F0w1m327s603G9G1L7K8O4.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gdlr-gal-1\" data-rel=\"fancybox\" ><img src=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x460/F7n8d021D0F0w1m327s603G9G1L7K8O4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"84\" /></a></div></div><div class=\"gallery-column three columns\"><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x422/R0g0b5g5E0l0H1Q3S7I6a3o9H1P8P5W9.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gdlr-gal-1\" data-rel=\"fancybox\" ><img src=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x422/R0g0b5g5E0l0H1Q3S7I6a3o9H1P8P5W9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"84\" /></a></div></div><div class=\"gallery-column three columns\"><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x422/h1X7J3O6t0Z0x1G3y776T3g9k1K829H0.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gdlr-gal-1\" data-rel=\"fancybox\" ><img src=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x422/h1X7J3O6t0Z0x1G3y776T3g9k1K829H0.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"84\" /></a></div></div><div class=\"gallery-column three columns\"><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x422/o0S048b9f0I0N1t3O7m6f3c9F1986852.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gdlr-gal-1\" data-rel=\"fancybox\" ><img src=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x422/o0S048b9f0I0N1t3O7m6f3c9F1986852.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"84\" /></a></div></div><div class=\"gallery-column three columns\"><div class=\"gallery-item\"><a href=\"http://www.nadmorski24.pl/images/632x422/k0f4i5H5y0w051I3r7S683D9L1h9C161.jpg\" data-fancybox-group=\"gdlr-gal-1\" data-rel=\"fancybox\" 